---
import { Facebook, Instagram } from "lucide-astro";
import IconButton from "../ui/IconButton.astro";
---

<div class="space-y-4 text-center sm:text-start">
  <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">Последвайте ни</p>
  <ul class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:justify-start">
    <li><IconButton><Facebook /></IconButton></li>
    <li><IconButton><Instagram /></IconButton></li>
    <li>
      <IconButton>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 448 512"
          fill="currentColor"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          ><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.6.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.-->
          <path
            d="M448 209.9a210.1 210.1 0 0 1 -122.8-39.3V349.4A162.6 162.6 0 1 1 185 188.3V278.2a74.6 74.6 0 1 0 52.2 71.2V0l88 0a121.2 121.2 0 0 0 1.9 22.2h0A122.2 122.2 0 0 0 381 102.4a121.4 121.4 0 0 0 67 20.1z"
          ></path></svg
        >
      </IconButton>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Тагни ни и има шанс да видиш <strong>своята снимка или видео</strong> в профила
    ни!
    <strong>#cocosolis</strong>
  </p>
</div>
